# Folder Structure Rules

- `app/` only for Expo Router files (screens/layouts/routes).
- `src/services/` contains API call code only; no React hooks/UI logic.
- `src/stores/` does not call APIs directly; call services instead.
- `src/components/common/` contains domain-agnostic reusable UI.
- Keep component files focused: one primary component per file.
- Use `@/` alias for deep imports.
